title: Crash in Redis 2.6 RC4 converting an hash value.

milestone.title: Redis 2.6
milestone.description: Redis 2.6, first version of Redis with scripting support.

body:
As received from Marty Weiner from Pinterest.

=== REDIS BUG REPORT START: Cut & paste starting from here ===

[10845] 09 Jun 04:42:08.251 # ==> t_hash.c:406 'ret == DICT_OK' is not true
